lukso-blockchain.Description:
LUKSO, the Blockchain for the new digital lifestyle is created by former Ethereum Developer Fabian Vogelsteller, author of ERC20 and web3.js.
LUKSO is a place where the worlds of fashion, gaming, design and social media intersect.

token-sale.Description: The sale of tokens to investors and speculators, in exchange for cryptocurrencies such as Ether.
